What's Your Astrological Sign?

Kateryna Savchyn
Sun Aug 23 13:12:10 2015

How It Works

It's extremely easy, you just put in the date you were born.

…that's pretty much it.

Based on your DOB, this web app tells you:

  • your element
  • your personality traits (both positive and negative) based on your sign
  • see if you agree or think this is dumb!

An Example

Here's an example of counts by astrological sign based on dates of birth for people born between Jan 1, 1969 and Dec 31, 1988 (from a dataset from Google's BigQuery, which I found here ). It turns out finding datasets with dates of birth down to the day is sort of hard and the original National Vital Statistics System (NVSS) datasets are massive, so thankfully I was able to find this guy's query.
